<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>爬山 - 标签 - 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%88%AC%E5%B1%B1/</link><description>爬山 - 标签 - 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><copyright>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Feb 2012 22:22:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%88%AC%E5%B1%B1/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>二月二</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/er-yue-er/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Feb 2012 22:22:00 +0000</pubDate><author><name>大大的小蜗牛</name><uri>https://eallion.com/</uri><email>eallions@gmail.com</email></author><guid>https://www.eallion.com/er-yue-er/</guid><description>文章讲述了作者在二月二这一天早上起来爬山烧香拜佛，感叹香炉峰的美景和香火旺盛。中午聚餐喝酒后剪了个龙头求签，待解的签文是关于坚持信心的。最后提到数字花园用爱发电。</description></item><item><title>踏青</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/ta-qing/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Feb 2012 16:08:00 +0000</pubDate><author><name>大大的小蜗牛</name><uri>https://eallion.com/</uri><email>eallions@gmail.com</email></author><guid>https://www.eallion.com/ta-qing/</guid><description>文章讲述了作者在一个阳光明媚的日子里，起床时不慎拉伤肩膀，经过治疗后勉强好转。然后作者决定去梅山公园晒太阳、散步和爬山。</description></item><item><title>山</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/mountain/</link><pubDate>Sun, 14 Dec 2008 19:58:41 +0000</pubDate><author><name>大大的小蜗牛</name><uri>https://eallion.com/</uri><email>eallions@gmail.com</email></author><guid>https://www.eallion.com/mountain/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了一个人在山上爬了一整天后，最后在唐安古寺帮着拖地，做了一些功德。文章以一种平和的口吻表达了作者对于这个人所做行为的赞美。</description></item></channel></rss>